@DATABASE "Moon Alert"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - M - Moon Alert"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - M
                   ====================================

                                Moon Alert
                                ==========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives  " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(39754,0)"}        39754,0
@{"Infinite Energy " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(42654,195)"}        42654,195
@{"Infinite Time   " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(42249,24)"}        42249,24
@{"Immediate scroll" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(42585,2) ZXAMPoke(42596,2)"}        42585,2:42596,2
@{"Lives = x       " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(42404,255)"}        42404,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         The only problem with the Infinite Time POKE is
                         that it takes AGES when you get your bonus
                         (just after the slightly dodgy copyright-infringing
                         Indiana Jones tune :) )

                         Rastan
@endnode
